      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "To project authority, focus on meticulous attention to detail in grooming. Hair should be neat, well-styled, and conservative, avoiding anything overly trendy. Clothing should be impeccably tailored, pressed, and coordinate colors in classic, powerful palettes like navy, charcoal, and slate. These deliberate choices signal competence and ensure the executive's focus remains on their expertise rather than their appearance.",
