      "content": "Got it. And what about other aspects of personal grooming? I've had a couple of clients ask about things like facial hair, piercings, or even religious attire—like hijabs or turbans. How do those fit into that \"polished and authoritative\" look you mentioned? Should they be trying to minimize those things to avoid being a distraction in the boardroom?",
