    "summary": "The user, acting as a corporate wellness coach, asks for advice on grooming and appearance to project authority in a boardroom. The assistant provides guidance on professional styling, specifically addressing textured hair and religious attire like hijabs or turbans to ensure they align with a \"polished\" look.",
